Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To your posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Make your way forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who brings me\Ntheir General's head will get a reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Bazuso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed 30 men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And a bear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want your head smashed in,\Nstep right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat him and you'll be famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too tough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn bunch of mercenaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to that coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His balls have shrunk up\Ninside of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Men! Have no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gouge out their eyes!\NPull out their innards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll feed them to the pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's he with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him act tough.\NHe'll get his head split open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He is fighting the Bazuso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for this scrap of iron here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We mercenaries, aren't knights.\NI can't feed myself with glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet against Bazuso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave words!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Bring him down and I'll\Ngive you seven pieces of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheap bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sorry, boy.\NYou're going to lose your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for seven pieces of silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Bazuso's getting pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? No one's done\Nthat to Bazuso before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put\Na stop to you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are definitely\Nthe better man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I. Bazuso am-!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bazuso's been!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! They've lost their confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's really something.\NI wonder who he's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away.\NWe just got here too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Blame it on that stupid general.\NIt's not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Griffith! I wonder\Nwho's stronger, you or him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask stupid questions.\NOf course. it's Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Two months' salary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and your reward for this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you won't reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's triple the salary, and maybe\Nyou'll even be a squire one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an impossible dream for\Nmost mercenaries, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream? You can't eat dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's guaranteed money and status.\NWhat's your problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate being restrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bandits. huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Corkus is shitting himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy's really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Him taking down Bazuso\Nwas no fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It was Corkus's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You started this!\NYou get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that length?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even pushing Casca back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful! He's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him. Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you sheathe your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! In just one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you'll stay alive\Nthat way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gambino! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He took in that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is how he pays him back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gambino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith should've just killed you\Nand left you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful to Casca.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She lay with you for two days
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep you warm after\Nyou lost all that blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On Griffith's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's a woman's job\Nto keep men warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it. Judeau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Griffith. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an amazing sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never wield it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So that bastard's up and around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a strange feeling...\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with the Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The last mercenaries you want\Nto face on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave us a lot of trouble\Nin the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're the Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a nice view!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you deliberately\Nmiss my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have done it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I want you, Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you swing that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your duel with Bazuso.\NIt was very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If his battle axe wasn't cracked...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have split your head open.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight like you're trying to see\Nhow much you can get away with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it looked like you were\Nintentionally exposing yourself to danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the same time.\Nyou're also struggling to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you, Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I refuse!\NTalking like you know everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,stabbing someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then acting like\Nyou're their friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle it with this.\NIf I win, I get to stab you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the chest just\Nlike you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make me your soldier or\Nyour piece of ass... do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind doing things by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, Casca.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I don't like about you.\NYou don't have any respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.47,0:24:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy just won't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith says stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this another day.\NYou're still weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Griffith!\N- That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.93,0:24:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do anything to win.\NI'm liking you more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't move your sword now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.44,0:24:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?\NYou can quit now if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure like to run your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But in a real fight,\Nyou have to use your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.78,0:24:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does your own blood taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.13,0:25:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet no one has ever hit that\Npretty face of yours before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.91,0:25:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to show you up\Nin front of your men,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.31,0:25:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but this ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes! He did it!\N- Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was effective...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.16,0:25:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.79,0:25:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.29,0:25:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'll dislocate your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.50,0:25:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.54,0:25:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man! He kicked his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.56,0:26:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.90,0:26:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never said that to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.54,0:26:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith has never said\Nthat to anyone before!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.38,0:26:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So now I'm in the Band of the Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, I'm going to have you fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For something dear to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.23,0:26:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get my own kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.47,0:26:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts. I'll be the one to decide\Nthe place where you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.87,0:27:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.37,0:27:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Show those Chuder dogs\Nwhat Midlanders are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape!\NKill anything that moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.78,0:28:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Their Black Ram Iron Lance Heavy Cavalry\Nis inflicting heavy damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.92,0:28:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate even our headquarters\Nhere may be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.49,0:28:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.80,0:28:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who can stop those\Nblack devils of Chuder?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.73,0:28:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.83,0:28:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Ram Iron Lance\NHeavy Cavalry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.97,0:28:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,will take the head of\Nthe King of Midland!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.81,0:28:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.98,0:28:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One man against all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then!\NI'll ride right over him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.77,0:29:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- He killed General Gien!\N- With one blow, by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.11,0:29:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alone! Surround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.71,0:29:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.22,0:29:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.82,0:29:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.45,0:29:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.22,0:29:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the Band of the Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.41,0:29:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The grim reapers of the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.18,0:29:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they fighting for Midland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.22,0:29:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuder is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.95,0:29:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.16,0:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One band of mercenaries can't possibly\Nturn the tide of the whole battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.53,0:30:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this "Band of the Hawk" strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.70,0:30:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They were well worth the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.43,0:30:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not put too much stock\Ninto one surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.57,0:30:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But they defeated the Black Rams,\Nwhen we could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.94,0:30:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the brilliance of their attack.\Nand how they anticipated the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.85,0:30:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who leads them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He is called Griffith. Sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.49,0:30:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Griffith"?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.68,0:30:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.48,0:31:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.19,0:31:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit too cool, maybe,\Nriding out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.22,0:31:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I shouldn't have\Ncharged them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.36,0:31:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he ever felt sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.27,0:31:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's not like the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.01,0:31:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we won. Let's celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.91,0:31:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Let's have a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.45,0:31:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.29,0:31:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Corkus?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Guts who did a great deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.16,0:31:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.16,0:31:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you.\NWill you give me a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.66,0:31:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Captain Guts, Sir"?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.47,0:31:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.81,0:31:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.84,0:31:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.15,0:32:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to be a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.32,0:32:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead you charged them\Nhead-on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked out well this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but you could have put\Nthe entire Band of the Hawk in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.46,0:32:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.44,0:32:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.84,0:32:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.87,0:32:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.24,0:32:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're satisfied just waving\Na sword around on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.38,0:32:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mad dog who never thinks\Nabout your comrades one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.62,0:32:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. I'm not like I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.86,0:32:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think about my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.00,0:32:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.50,0:32:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.34,0:32:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak to Guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.15,0:33:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too easy on him, Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.42,0:33:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You two really don't get along, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.92,0:33:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me.\NShe's always on my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.86,0:33:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been like this for three years.\NGive it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.67,0:33:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since you and I fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.37,0:33:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.98,0:33:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that kind of fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.52,0:33:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. You're the man of\Nthe hour tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.16,0:33:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.90,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... about today's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.03,0:34:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, fight for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.90,0:34:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.29,0:34:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about Lord Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.76,0:34:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is most disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true we have not been defeated\Nsince the Band of the Hawk joined us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.67,0:34:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are mercenaries,\Nled by a man who can be bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Without war.\Nthey are nothing but bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To elevate riff-raff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.71,0:34:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The low-born are low-born.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good can come about from\Ntreating them as something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But without them, Chuder might\Nhave destroyed us by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.09,0:35:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand why His Majesty\Nwould have gone to all this trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.60,0:35:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.03,0:35:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. but still.\NRaising a commoner to nobility...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.67,0:35:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an eccentric choice by His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.01,0:35:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the Band of the Hawk led\Nour armies in the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.08,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what of Count Julius and\Nhis White Dragon Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.42,0:35:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.18,0:35:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The ransom was quite high\Nwhen Chuder took him prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.11,0:35:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy Count is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.34,0:35:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gut's Raiders are still inside\Nmopping up the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.15,0:35:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual for it to\Nbe taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.52,0:35:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this castle\Nwould be this hard to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.05,0:36:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you report sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said there was\Ntreasure deep inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we started hearing screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.00,0:36:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No one came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.27,0:36:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! I'll go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.80,0:36:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, Gaston!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.24,0:36:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go ask General Griffith\Nfor reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.71,0:36:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that and I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.14,0:36:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.11,0:36:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.42,0:37:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to these corpses?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.09,0:37:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.32,0:37:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.66,0:37:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu Zodd?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.46,0:37:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. it looks like he's on\Nthe enemy's side in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zodd, you mean\Nthe legendary swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you could fill a whole country\Nwith the heads he's taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.80,0:38:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not feared just\Nbecause he's powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.71,0:38:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The tales of his achievements\Nin battle go back 200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.78,0:38:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,200 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.72,0:38:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they call him\NNosferatu Zodd.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.09,0:38:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong! Too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.23,0:38:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have done well, boy,\Nto stand against me for this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.97,0:38:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.54,0:38:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the swords alone are\Nevenly matched, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.73,0:39:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.90,0:39:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were aiming for my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.67,0:39:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first man to drive\Ntheir sword this deeply into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.62,0:39:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To stand against\Nan enemy like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.92,0:39:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably why I have survived\Nfor these 300 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.97,0:39:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.64,0:39:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster like this exists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.98,0:39:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.95,0:39:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not disappoint me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.24,0:40:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should say you have\Ndone well for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.61,0:40:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Zodd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.21,0:40:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay focused! Second volley!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.85,0:40:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.50,0:40:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No one shall defile this fight,\Nno matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.67,0:40:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.68,0:40:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca, have everyone withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith! Where is?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.79,0:41:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.06,0:41:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.59,0:41:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for when we get away\Nfrom that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you are shredded into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.37,0:41:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.91,0:41:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.84,0:41:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.28,0:41:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't. we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.08,0:41:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.68,0:41:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.93,0:41:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts! We'll make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.57,0:41:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.21,0:41:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I would meet two men\Non the same day who can wound me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.01,0:42:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and then have to lose them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.35,0:42:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.92,0:42:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.02,0:42:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,my...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.59,0:42:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell. human!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.74,0:42:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Egg of the King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.11,0:42:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the Crimson Behelit\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.92,0:42:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So it's that kind of trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.26,0:42:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I will give you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.46,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.50,0:43:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a true friend\Nto this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.34,0:43:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,take heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.84,0:43:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When his ambition dies within him...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,death will come to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.92,0:43:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A death you cannot escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.97,0:43:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.67,0:43:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.14,0:43:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.55,0:43:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A "true friend"?\NI'm going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.75,0:43:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.\NJust what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.32,0:43:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.42,0:43:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.53,0:43:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.83,0:44:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault this happened\Nto Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.04,0:44:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.92,0:44:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.56,0:44:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a mad dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.30,0:44:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault this happened\Nto Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.90,0:44:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.74,0:44:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.25,0:44:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is she\Ntalking about?! That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.45,0:44:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurt worse than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.09,0:44:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.49,0:45:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu Zodd?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.33,0:45:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster like that in this world?\NThat's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.07,0:45:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at it another way,\Nit might prove...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.14,0:45:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the existence of something\Nthat we can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.41,0:45:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.48,0:45:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be more like the Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.08,0:45:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.82,0:45:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it.\Nthat thing around your neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.73,0:45:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When that monster saw it.\Nhe took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.77,0:45:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A Behelit. An old fortune teller\Ngave it to me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.98,0:45:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it's the destiny of one\Nwho holds it to acquire the world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.38,0:45:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in exchange for\Nhis flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.15,0:46:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The world. huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.34,0:46:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing gives me the creeps!\NDon't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.55,0:46:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's neat. huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.76,0:46:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That part of you never changes,\Ndoes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.83,0:46:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.14,0:46:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.21,0:46:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a soldier,\Na subordinate at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.41,0:47:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.02,0:47:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.45,0:47:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason every time\NI put myself in harm's way for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.10,0:47:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.37,0:47:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your wounds healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.51,0:47:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.72,0:47:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.49,0:47:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in the king's presence!\NYou're being disrespectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.31,0:48:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.08,0:48:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Griffith, your Band of\Nthe Hawk is doing magnificent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.28,0:48:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, should you speak thusly\Nto one so new with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.39,0:48:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.83,0:48:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. there are some who\Ndo not think well
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.53,0:48:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of these men of common birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.90,0:48:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But dignity and status\Ndo not win battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.94,0:48:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have great hopes for you,\Nunfettered by tradition as you all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.11,0:48:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.42,0:48:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.46,0:48:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.76,0:48:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she does not like warriors,\Nand rarely comes outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.76,0:49:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.07,0:49:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my only child.\NPerhaps I've spoilt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.01,0:49:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must forgive me Count Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.28,0:49:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.57,0:49:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.58,0:49:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.28,0:49:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.05,0:49:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.02,0:49:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you touch the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.73,0:50:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you old...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.96,0:50:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, Your Lordship General Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.97,0:50:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you understand,\Nit's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.64,0:50:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, your father awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.18,0:50:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.60,0:50:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we wasting time with\Nthese nobles and their sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.37,0:50:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.11,0:50:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the job.\NAnd it beats being on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.31,0:50:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No arrows, no heads split open...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.95,0:51:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this thing suits me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.62,0:51:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes...\Nbloodthirsty madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.82,0:51:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again, Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.19,0:51:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.39,0:51:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing guard at the hunt has\Nalways been reserved for knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.76,0:51:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.83,0:51:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we've all fought for\Nin the mud of the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.61,0:51:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're calling it stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.31,0:51:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.01,0:51:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to wave around your sword,\Ngo do it alone, you madman!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.99,0:51:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To each his own, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.76,0:51:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.41,0:52:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like to hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do gentlemen enjoy bloodshed?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.09,0:52:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In war, and in hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.07,0:52:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.11,0:52:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.83,0:52:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,General...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.90,0:52:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wait for our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.23,0:52:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.80,0:52:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After it!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.69,0:53:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.77,0:53:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.61,0:53:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.35,0:53:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.46,0:53:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.30,0:54:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.07,0:54:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart's pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.57,0:54:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.64,0:54:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be calming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.88,0:54:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back.\NEveryone will be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.35,0:54:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.62,0:54:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.12,0:54:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.13,0:54:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.27,0:54:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.38,0:54:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.24,0:54:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.38,0:54:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?\NWhere did the arrow come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.78,0:54:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.05,0:54:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith! Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.49,0:54:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Casca.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.86,0:55:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Griffith!\N- Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.93,0:55:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The arrow. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.57,0:55:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.40,0:55:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.57,0:55:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.47,0:55:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.77,0:55:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This shielded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.48,0:55:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Egg of the King...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.35,0:55:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.35,0:55:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.78,0:55:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's devil's luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.12,0:55:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.59,0:55:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not "luck."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.19,0:55:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.03,0:55:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go search those bushes\Nwith some men.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.40,0:55:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your armor. We have to\Nmake sure you're not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.62,0:55:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.65,0:56:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,will cost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.06,0:56:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.56,0:56:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.68,0:56:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you hope to lead\Nmy White Dragon Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.15,0:56:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.95,0:56:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.12,0:56:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father! I can continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.76,0:56:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see to that wound. Master Adonis.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.73,0:56:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, in his youth,\Nwas the product
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.50,0:56:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of very severe training.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.67,0:56:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not hold this against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.64,0:56:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.91,0:57:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The second in line to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.05,0:57:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The General of the White Dragons,\NCount Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.15,0:57:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison on the arrow\Nmeant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.06,0:57:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is one this royal house has used\Nfor generations, for assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.86,0:57:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.63,0:57:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.24,0:57:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.78,0:57:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I am asking you.\NWill you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.55,0:57:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.69,0:57:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me an order like\Nyou always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.16,0:57:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging your pardon, Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.29,0:57:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps you are being a little\Ntoo rough on the young master?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.90,0:57:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Hassan!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.73,0:57:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Adonis cannot stay a child forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.20,0:57:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When he succeeds me.\Nhe must be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.94,0:58:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.97,0:58:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.96,0:58:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did I fail, but he's now\Na hero for saving the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.98,0:58:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.04,0:58:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hassan!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.02,0:58:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,An intruder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.21,0:59:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.88,0:59:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... Griffith's!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.49,1:00:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.39,1:01:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.59,1:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.03,1:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An intruder!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.33,1:01:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.80,1:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Adonis!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.23,1:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.87,1:01:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.04,1:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.37,1:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.71,1:01:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He should still be close!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.44,1:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.92,1:01:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Adonis. too! How brutal!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.23,1:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him! Don't let him escape alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.51,1:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! He's on the west wall!\NCut him off there!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.96,1:02:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.15,1:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Griffith is eating better stuff\Nthan this at the Princess's banquet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.82,1:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. but with that bunch\Nhe won't be able to relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.43,1:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.20,1:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get to eat fine food,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.90,1:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and get lucky with\Nsome perfumed noble lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.97,1:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a little stress?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.07,1:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lucky with a noble lady at\NPrincess Charlotte's banquet?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.91,1:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.68,1:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Guts?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.72,1:03:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.05,1:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably off practicing again.\NThat bloodthirsty madman.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.76,1:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Another, Pippin...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.02,1:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He was supposed to train with\Nmy unit today.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.40,1:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't show up.\NWithout a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.44,1:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.18,1:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.31,1:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been all day?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.55,1:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.95,1:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte invited him...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.99,1:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to her banquet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.06,1:03:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be at Promrose Hall...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.43,1:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.30,1:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm not done talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.07,1:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.38,1:04:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An arrow wound?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.95,1:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice breeze!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.28,1:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never grown accustomed to\Nevents like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.82,1:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.20,1:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Princess Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.60,1:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.17,1:05:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.89,1:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.35,1:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going in like that?\NDon't embarrass Griffith.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.89,1:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait until they're finished talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.90,1:05:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.17,1:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.05,1:05:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you asked me\Nwhy men are so fond...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.38,1:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.29,1:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.42,1:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true it might simply be\Na barbaric side to their nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.19,1:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But that allows men to preserve\Nsomething that is dear to their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.73,1:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sword that cuts both ways.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.24,1:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear to their hearts"?\NLike a lover?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.01,1:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant... something like honor?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are important.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.18,1:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A true knight fights and dies\Nfor both love and honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.95,1:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But a man should encounter\None more thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.76,1:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that is dear to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.36,1:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.83,1:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream he must realize for\Nhimself and himself alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.41,1:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.81,1:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who you are,\Nit's a dream that sets you on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.78,1:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream that sustains you,\Noppresses you, keeps you alive...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.89,1:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then kills you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.63,1:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after the dream abandons you,\Nit still smoulders in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.83,1:07:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At least once.\Na man should have a vision of that life...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.37,1:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as a martyr to the god named Dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.98,1:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To simply live a life because\None was born into it...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.85,1:07:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.03,1:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. This must be such\Na boring topic for a lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.63,1:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.57,1:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.70,1:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a very mysterious gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.21,1:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nobler than any nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.38,1:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you showed me how\Nto play the leaf whistle,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.38,1:08:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you were like a child playing\Nin the fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.45,1:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're like a philosopher.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.26,1:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.47,1:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this charm is what attracted\Nyour friends to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.37,1:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They are precious comrades who\Nhave faced death with me many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.18,1:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are not friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.98,1:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend is someone who does not\Ncling to another's dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.72,1:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He decides his own.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.85,1:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and he will stand against anyone
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.09,1:08:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,who dares to trample\Non it with his body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.86,1:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that person is me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.16,1:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend to me, is an equal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.95,1:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith.\Nso what is this dream of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.29,1:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.83,1:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.47,1:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.54,1:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Uncle Count Julius. has died!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.84,1:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.24,1:09:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an assassination!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.58,1:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone crept into his home\Nand murdered him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.85,1:09:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His son Master Adonis. too!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.05,1:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle's in an uproar!\NThe banquet has been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.65,1:09:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty orders you\Nto return home at once!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.76,1:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your escort is coming.\NPlease prepare to depart!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.80,1:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. There'll be war if\Nthis is Chuder's handiwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.90,1:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.81,1:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.95,1:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How to fight, how to kill...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.82,1:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.26,1:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be his sword!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.63,1:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a castle that's\Na little bit bigger. So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.57,1:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what Griffith says,\Nand it will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.68,1:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Risk your life!\NThat's the only way you'll survive!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.25,1:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we survive. we win!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.13,1:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see what Griffith\Nand the Band of the Hawk were up to.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.00,1:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who they brought with them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.33,1:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and what else they were after.

